      <t>   This document provides clarity about how PCEP operates and hence to
   facilitates interoperability between different equipment vendors.
   The content of this document has been compiled based on the feedback
   from several multi-vendor interop exercises.  Several constructs are
   introduced, such as the LSP-DB and the ASSO-DB.


